 * docker attach --no-stdin mycontainer # connects but cuts out stdin(your keyboard) - usecase: for watching log file and muting yourself incase you accidentally press a button
 * docker logs  -f iwemida #-f flag means follow, so new log lines keep appearing in real time # the code shows the logs of the container.



